Name: Reggero

Phone usage without limitations. With Reggero that will not be the problem. Your speakers will be lifted and will provide you with full sound effects..

Name: Aleccia
Description: Aleccia - Comfortable women's sandals. Comfortable and airy steps throughout the summer! The ergonomic model with a small platform provides great support for your feet. Name: Alora
Description: Alora - Spiritual necklace with a medallion. A beautiful piece of jewelry believed to bring special graces to the Virgin Mary. It exudes divine beauty and carries strong symbolism. Perfect for all those who want to get closer to their faith and respect the Blessed Mother.. History and meaning of the medallion with the Virgin Mary. The origin of the miraculous medallion dates back to 1830. when the young nun in Paris repeatedly saw the Blessed Mother presented to her within an oval frame with rays from her hands, with the inscription: O Mary, conceived without sin, pray for us who turn to you." When she asked Mary about these rays, she replied, "These are graces that people forget to seek." The nun said that Mary asked her to bring these visions and words to others in the form of a protective medallion, so that "All who wear them will receive great graces.". Powerful symbolism. The main significance of this piece of jewelry is the belief that wearing it will bring special graces from the Virgin Mary. It is often worn to strengthen a person’s faith in the Catholic tradition, but it can be worn by anyone who has a Christian affiliation and respects the Blessed Mother. The medal is also worn by those who want to get closer to their faith or those who are going through difficult times in life.. Important principles of the Christian faith. The Virgin Mary is always depicted on the front of the miraculous medallion. On the back of the medallion is the sign M, surmounted by a cross, with two hearts and 12 stars. "M" stands for "Mary." The cross represents the sacrifice of Jesus. Two hearts are for the immaculate heart of the Virgin Mary and for the holy heart of Jesus. The 12 stars symbolize the 12 apostles.. Original production. Although there are many variations, this necklace with a medallion was made exactly according to the original instructions of the nun who made the first such necklaces. The chain and medallion are made of quality copper and covered with gold color protection. It symbolizes the precious graces of the Blessed Virgin, available only to those who truly believe.. Quality and durability. The Alora necklace with a medallion is made to last and to stand securely around your neck. The Blessed Virgin will be closer to your heart in this way, which has a special symbolism. A carefully crafted necklace will firmly guard this precious medallion around your neck and will look beautiful at any occasion. Also, this is an exceptional gift for true Christians.."
